This project was initiated by the U54 Partnership between Ponce Health Sciences University
and Moffitt Cancer Center. Dr. Cress (MCC) is leading this project to evaluate breast
cancer tumors assembled into a tissue microarray from a broad representation of
the population, including patients from Puerto Rico and Tampa Bay area.
